cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset, please cite it as below."
title: "ByteCosts AI Pricing Index"
abstract: >-
  A source-linked index of AI model pricing. Each row records a provider's
  per-token input/output price with the provider source URL it was read from and
  the date that price was last verified. The 2026-06-14 snapshot holds 300
  source-derived rows across 39 represented providers, derived from a broader
  ByteCosts catalog tracking 5,261 models across 145 providers.
type: dataset
authors:
  - name: "ByteCosts"
    website: "https://bytecosts.com"
url: "https://bytecosts.com/data/ai-pricing-dataset/"
repository-code: "https://github.com/erson/ai-pricing-index"
license: CC-BY-4.0
version: "2026.06.14"
date-released: "2026-06-14"
keywords:
  - "AI model pricing"
  - "LLM pricing"
  - "API pricing"
  - "cost estimation"
  - "tokens"
